column2: bslNPChla_plot_3 <- ggplot(bslNPChla_wide, aes(x=N, y=chla)) + geom_point() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) + ggtitle("N (mg/L) vs Chla (ug/L) in Big Spirit Lake From 2002-2022") + geom_smooth(method=lm) + xlab("N (mg/L)") + ylab("Chlorophyll a (ug/L)")
